id.description:

Trailer Spider-Man: Brand New Day https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B_59lBNjosE&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Video Terbaru Keren https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

Meliputi Teaser Avengers Doomsday Terbaru. Penjelasan Doctor Doom vs Thor & Captain Marvel. Teaser Avengers Doomsday NYCC & Panel Comic Con. X-Men yang Akurat dari Komik, Robert Downey Jr. Doctor Doom. Fantastic Four bertemu The Avengers, Bocoran Trailer Avengers Doomsday D23, dan Telur Paskah. Karakter baru, Rencana Induk Doctor Doom, Deadpool, Spider-Man. Proyek Deadpool baru Ryan Reynolds, film-film X-Force, Avengers Doomsday, rencana Secret Wars. Rencana X-Men untuk Avengers 6 Secret Wars dijelaskan. Saga Mutasi Marvel Fase 7, film-film X-Men baru.

Mengapa Ryan Reynolds dituntut atas Deadpool dan Wolverine. Lelucon Marvel, adegan yang dihapus, gugatan Ryan Reynolds dan Blake Lively. Apa yang akan terjadi sebagai akibatnya. Dan mengapa Ryan Reynolds tidak perlu khawatir. Dan bagaimana Marvel, Deadpool, dan Wolverine menjadi bagian dari gugatan tersebut.

X-23, Wolverine vs Hulk, adegan Gambit yang dihapus, adegan Blade yang dihapus, Sabretooth, Wolverine vs Sabretooth. Lelucon Deadpool vs Disney, Lelucon Marvel Kevin Feige dan Pecahnya Tembok Keempat. Lelucon Adegan Pasca-Kredit Deadpool dan Wolverine. Adegan Iron Man Jahat, Adegan Cameo The Punisher, Adegan X-Men, Varian Deadpool Lainnya, Varian Wolverine Lainnya. Penjelasan Adamantium. Referensi Ben Affleck tentang Daredevil, Elektra, Mengapa Deadpool Menyelamatkan Wolverine, X-Men, Fantastic Four, dan Deadpool Menyelamatkan MCU. Bagaimana Deadpool dan Wolverine mempersiapkan Avengers 6 Secret Wars dengan Battleworld dan Loki Musim 2 Berakhir dengan Easter Egg Crossover God Loki

Mengapa Marvel me-reboot MCU, semua film Marvel dan acara TV Disney plus Marvel dengan Avengers 6 Secret Wars. Dan apa yang akan berubah dengan semua Avengers, New Iron Man, Mutan X-Men seperti Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man, dan karakter Marvel lainnya yang sebelumnya tidak dapat digunakan seperti yang mereka inginkan di film-film sebelumnya.

Banyak Trailer Marvel lainnya segera hadir: Trailer Avengers 5 Doomsday, Trailer Thunderbolts, Trailer Avengers 6 Secret Wars & video Trailer Spider-Man Brand New Day! Video Trailer NYCC juga akan hadir minggu ini!

Un nuovo teaser di Avengers Doomsday. Dottor Destino contro Thor e Captain Marvel spiegati. Teaser di Avengers Doomsday al NYCC e panel del Comic-Con. X-Men fedeli ai fumetti, Dottor Destino di Robert Downey Jr. I Fantastici Quattro incontrano gli Avengers, analisi delle fughe di notizie del trailer di Avengers Doomsday al D23 e Easter Egg. Nuovi personaggi, il piano generale del Dottor Destino, Deadpool, Spider-Man. Nuovo progetto di Ryan Reynolds su Deadpool, film sulla X-Force, Avengers: Doomsday, piani per Secret Wars. Spiegazione del piano di Avengers 6 Secret Wars per gli X-Men. Saga dei Mutanti della Fase 7 della Marvel, nuovi film sugli X-Men.

Perch√© Ryan Reynolds √® stato citato in giudizio per Deadpool e Wolverine. Battute Marvel, scene eliminate, causa tra Ryan Reynolds e Blake Lively. Cosa succeder√† di conseguenza. E perch√© Ryan Reynolds non deve preoccuparsi. E come la Marvel, Deadpool e Wolverine sono stati coinvolti nella causa.

X-23, Wolverine contro Hulk, scene eliminate di Gambit, scene eliminate di Blade, Sabretooth, Wolverine contro Sabretooth. Battute su Deadpool contro Disney, battute su Kevin Feige e rottura della quarta parete. Battute sulla scena post-credit di Deadpool e Wolverine. Scena di Iron Man malvagio, scena del cameo di The Punisher, scene degli X-Men, altre varianti di Deadpool, altre varianti di Wolverine. Spiegazione dell'Adamantio. Riferimenti a Daredevil con Ben Affleck, Elektra, perch√© Deadpool salva Wolverine, gli X-Men, i Fantastici Quattro e Deadpool salvano l'MCU. Come Deadpool e Wolverine preparano Avengers 6 Secret Wars con Battleworld e il finale della seconda stagione di Loki con Easter Egg del crossover con Dio Loki.

Perch√© la Marvel sta riavviando l'MCU, tutti i film Marvel e le serie TV Disney e Marvel con Avengers 6 Secret Wars. E cosa cambier√† con tutti gli Avengers, il Nuovo Iron Man, gli X-Men, i Mutanti come Wolverine, Deadpool, i Fantastici Quattro, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man e altri personaggi Marvel che non erano stati in grado di usare come avrebbero voluto nei film precedenti?

Molti altri trailer Marvel presto: il trailer di Avengers 5 Doomsday, il trailer di Thunderbolts, il trailer di Avengers 6 Secret Wars e il trailer di Spider-Man Brand New Day! Anche i trailer del NYCC arriveranno questa settimana!

Bekijk de nieuwe teaser van Avengers Doomsday. Doctor Doom vs. Thor & Captain Marvel uitgelegd. Avengers Doomsday NYCC teaser & Comic Con panel. Comic Book Accurate X-Men, Robert Downey Jr. Doctor Doom. Fantastic Four ontmoet The Avengers, Avengers Doomsday trailer D23 lekanalyse en easter eggs. Nieuwe personages, Doctor Dooms masterplan, Deadpool, Spider-Man. Ryan Reynolds' nieuwe Deadpool-project, X-Force-films, Avengers Doomsday, Secret Wars-plannen. Avengers 6 Secret Wars X-Men-plan uitgelegd. Marvel Phase 7 Mutant Saga, nieuwe X-Men-films.

Waarom Ryan Reynolds werd aangeklaagd voor Deadpool en Wolverine. Marvel-grappen, verwijderde sc√®nes, rechtszaak Ryan Reynolds en Blake Lively. Wat er gaat gebeuren. En waarom Ryan Reynolds zich geen zorgen hoeft te maken. En hoe Marvel, Deadpool en Wolverine onderdeel werden van de rechtszaak.

X-23, Wolverine vs Hulk, verwijderde sc√®nes in Gambit, verwijderde sc√®nes in Blade, Sabretooth, Wolverine vs Sabretooth. Deadpool vs Disney-grappen, Kevin Feige Marvel-grappen en het doorbreken van de Vierde Muur. Deadpool en Wolverine-grappen na de aftiteling. Evil Iron Man-sc√®ne, cameosc√®ne in The Punisher, X-Men-sc√®nes, meer Deadpool-varianten, meer Wolverine-varianten. Adamantium uitgelegd. Ben Affleck Daredevil-referenties, Elektra, waarom Deadpool Wolverine redt, de X-Men, Fantastic Four en Deadpool redt de MCU. Hoe Deadpool en Wolverine Avengers 6 Secret Wars voorbereiden met Battleworld en Loki Seizoen 2 eindigt met God Loki Crossover Easter Eggs.

Waarom Marvel de MCU reboot, alle Marvel-films en Disney Plus Marvel-tv-series met Avengers 6 Secret Wars. En wat gaat er veranderen met al de Avengers, New Iron Man, X-Men-mutanten zoals Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man en andere personages die Marvel eerder niet op de gewenste manier kon gebruiken in eerdere films?

Binnenkort veel meer Marvel-trailers: Avengers 5 Doomsday-trailer, Thunderbolts-trailer, Avengers 6 Secret Wars-trailer & Spider-Man gloednieuwe trailervideo's! NYCC-trailervideo's komen deze week ook!

snippet.title: Bel-Air | Final Season | Official Trailer | Peacock Original
snippet.description:
New Season of Bel-Air is streaming November 24 on Peacock, plus catch up on Seasons 1-3 streaming now: https://pck.tv/33jMKRk

Synopsis: In season four of Peacock‚Äôs ‚ÄúBel-Air,‚Äù Will tries to balance the fun and excitement of senior year with the expectations that have brought him to this moment. Carlton tests his own resolve as he deals with the fallout of some very big decisions that could threaten his future. Together, both boys will help each other through this pivotal time in their lives. An unexpected power shift will threaten the brotherhood between Phil and Geoffrey, whose loyalties to the Banks family will be tested. Viv struggles with reinventing herself as she looks at motherhood from a different perspective. It‚Äôs Ashley‚Äôs freshman year in high school and she‚Äôs working through a rebellious phase but quickly learns that the status quo may no longer serve her. Hilary goes on a journey of self-exploration.

#Peacock #BelAir #OfficialTrailer

With the streaming service from NBCUniversal, you can watch new movies from theaters, current hits from NBC and Bravo, nonstop action from WWE, Premier League, Big Ten, and tons of other sports. üìñ Lyrics: SZA - Good Days

[Verse 1: SZA]
Good day in my mind, safe to take a step out
Get some air now, let‚ÄÖyo‚ÄÖedge out
Too soon,‚ÄÖI spoke
You be heavy in my‚ÄÖmind, can you get the heck out?
I need rest now, got me bummed out
You so, you so, you
Baby, baby, babe
I've been on my empty mind shit

[Pre-Chorus: SZA]
I try to keep from losin' the rest of me
I worry that I wasted the best of me on you, babe
You don't care
Said, "Not tryna be a nuisance, this is urgent"
Tryna make sense of loose change
Got me a war in my mind
Gotta let go of weight, can't keep what's holdin' me
Choose to watch while the world break up in front of me

[Chorus: SZA, Jacob Collier & Both]
All the while, I'll await my armored fate with a smile
I still wanna try, still believe in
Good days, good days, always
Always inside (Always in my mind, always in my mind, mind)
Good day living in my mind

[Verse 2: SZA, Jacob Collier]
Tell me I'm not my fears, my limitations
I disappear if you let me
Feelin' like, yeah (On your own)
Feelin' like Jericho
Feelin' like Job when he lost his shit
Gotta hold my own, my cross to bear alone, I
Ooh, played and dipped, way to kill the mood
Know you like that shit
Can't groove it, ba-baby
Heavy on my empty mind shit

[Pre-Chorus: SZA]
I gotta keep from losin' the rest of me (Rest of me)
Still worry that I wasted the best of me on you, babe
You don't care
Said, "Not tryna be a nuisance, this is urgent" (It's urgent)
Tryna make sense of loose change
Got me a war in my mind (My mind)
Gotta let go of weight, can't keep what's holdin' me
Choose to watch while the world break up in front of me

[Chorus: SZA, Jacob Collier & Both]
All the while, I'll await my armored fate with a smile
I still wanna try, still believe in
Good days, good days, always (Good days on my mind, good days on my mind)
Sunny inside (Always in my mind, always in my mind, mind)
Good day living in my mind

[Verse 3: SZA]
Gotta get right
Tryna free my mind before the end of the world
I don't miss no ex, I don't miss no text
I choose not to respond
I don't regret, just pretend shit never happened
Half of us layin' waste to our youth, it's in the present
(Na-na, na-na, na-na, na)
Half of us chasin' fountains of youth and it's in the present now

[Outro: Jacob Collier]
Always in my mind, always in my mind, mind
You've been making me feel like I'm
Always in my mind, always in my mind, mind

About SlisTeaser:
SlisTeaser create trailer mashups‚Äîalso known as recut trailers‚Äîby combining scenes from one or more movies to craft new, imaginative trailers.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Pearl Jam - Black (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Pearl Jam - Black (Lyrics)


üîî Turn on notifications to stay updated with new uploads!

Lyrics:

[Intro]
Hey-hey-hey
Yeah-ah

[Verse 1]
Sheets of empty canvas, untouched sheets of clay
Her lace spread out before me, as her body once did
All five horizons revolved around her soul, as the Earth to the Sun
Now the air I tasted and breathed has taken a turn

[Pre-Chorus]
Ooh-oh, and all I taught her was everything
Mmm, oh, I know she gave me all that she wore

[Chorus 1]
And now my bitter hands chafe beneath the clouds
Of what was everything
All the pictures have all been washed in black
Tattooed everything

[Verse 2]
I take a walk outside, I'm surrounded by some kids at play
I can feel their laughter, so why do I see her?

[Pre-Chorus]
Mmm-hmm, all the twisted thoughts that spin 'round my head
I'm spinnin', oh, I'm spinnin'
How quick the Sun can drop away

[Chorus 2]
And now my bitter hands cradle broken glass
Of what was everything
All the pictures have all been washed in black
Tattooed everything

[Post-Chorus]
All the love gone bad, turned my world to black
Tattooed all I see, all that I am, all that I'll be, yeah
Uh-huh
(Uh-huh, ooh)

[Bridge]
I know someday you'll have a beautiful life, I know you'll be a star
In somebody else's sky, but why? Why?
Why can't it be? Oh, can't it be mine?
(Doo-doo-doo-doo, doo-doo-doo)
Ooh, ah, yeah
Ah, ooh-ooh

[Outro]

Brettski couldn‚Äôt believe his eyes. Wedged between the seats of his old filming car‚Äîa crumpled $5,000 casino voucher from months ago. He stared at it, laughing in disbelief. ‚ÄúAin‚Äôt no way,‚Äù he muttered. The expiration date? Today. The universe had just thrown him a bone, or maybe a setup.

He raced to the casino, heart pounding like the bonus music on a Dragon Link. Cameras charged, mic clipped, that signature Brettski grin locked in. ‚ÄúLet‚Äôs see if the gambling gods are real,‚Äù he said, striding through the doors like a man on a mission.

His first machine? A $25 spin on Lightning Cash. Bang‚Äîbonus. $3,600 win. The crowd behind him started cheering. ‚ÄúHe‚Äôs back!‚Äù someone yelled. He switched to Buffalo Gold, dropped to $50 spins‚Äîdead spins. Then another. Then another. The $8,600 total melted to $4,200 in minutes.

‚ÄúOkay‚Ä¶ we‚Äôre in danger,‚Äù he whispered. Then, in pure Brettski fashion, he shoved the TITO slip into the high-limit room. A $100 bet per spin, eyes locked on the screen. Nothing. Then‚ÄîBANG‚Äîthree moons. Bonus. He leaned forward, eyes wide. Each spin added more moons, multipliers stacking. $1,000‚Ä¶ $3,000‚Ä¶ $9,000‚Ä¶ then the Grand symbol flashed once, twice‚Äî

‚Äîand disappeared.

The bonus ended at $14,700. Brettski threw his hands up. ‚ÄúThat‚Äôs the buyback money right there!‚Äù he laughed. He stood, ready to cash out, when the attendant walked over. ‚ÄúHey sir, quick question,‚Äù she said. ‚ÄúThat voucher you used‚Ä¶ where‚Äôd you find it?‚Äù

He froze.

‚ÄúBecause,‚Äù she continued, glancing at her tablet, ‚Äúthat $5,000 slip was reported missing months ago‚Ä¶ and it wasn‚Äôt yours.‚Äù

The lights above flickered. Security appeared at the edge of the room. Brettski‚Äôs smile faded as the slot screens around him began to glitch‚Äîshowing his face on every monitor.

To be continued‚Ä¶

id.title: Saya Tiba-tiba Menemukan $5000, Jadi Saya Mempertaruhkannya Semua!
id.description:
Kami KEMBALI ke Kasino, dan NATAL BARU SAJA DATANG LEBIH AWAL! Saya menemukan $5.000 secara acak, jadi JELAS kita akan mempertaruhkannya! Terima kasih banyak sudah menonton. Kalian semua cantik, dan saya sangat menghargai kalian semua yang telah ikut serta dalam perjalanan gila ini. Doakan saya beruntung, dan sampai jumpa di yang berikutnya! Ayo berperang!

Mainkan slot dan permainan meja favorit Anda sepenuhnya gratis di: https://spinquest.com/?u=brettski

Brettski tak percaya apa yang dilihatnya. Terjepit di antara kursi mobil syuting lamanya‚Äîsebuah voucher kasino $5.000 yang kusut dari beberapa bulan lalu. Ia menatapnya, tertawa tak percaya. "Mana mungkin," gumamnya. Tanggal kedaluwarsa? Hari ini. Semesta baru saja memberinya hadiah, atau mungkin jebakan.

Ia berlari ke kasino, jantungnya berdebar kencang seperti musik bonus di Dragon Link. Kamera terisi penuh, mikrofon terjepit, seringai khas Brettski terpatri. "Mari kita lihat apakah dewa judi itu nyata," katanya, melangkah masuk seperti orang yang sedang menjalankan misi.

Mesin pertamanya? Putaran $25 di Lightning Cash. Bang‚Äîbonus. Kemenangan $3.600. Penonton di belakangnya mulai bersorak. "Dia kembali!" teriak seseorang. Dia beralih ke Buffalo Gold, putarannya turun menjadi $50‚Äîputaran mati. Lalu satu putaran lagi. Lalu satu putaran lagi. Total $8.600 mencair menjadi $4.200 dalam hitungan menit.

"Oke... kita dalam bahaya," bisiknya. Lalu, dengan gaya Brettski yang khas, dia memasukkan slip TITO ke dalam ruangan berbatas tinggi. Taruhan $100 per putaran, mata terpaku pada layar. Tidak ada apa-apa. Lalu‚ÄîBANG‚Äîtiga bulan. Bonus. Dia mencondongkan tubuh ke depan, matanya terbelalak. Setiap putaran menambahkan lebih banyak bulan, pengalinya menumpuk. $1.000‚Ä¶ $3.000‚Ä¶ $9.000‚Ä¶ lalu simbol Grand berkedip sekali, dua kali‚Äî

‚Äîdan menghilang.

Bonus berakhir di $14.700. Brettski mengangkat tangannya. "Itu uang pembelian kembalinya!" ia tertawa. Ia berdiri, siap untuk mencairkan uang, ketika petugas datang. "Hei, Pak, pertanyaan singkat," katanya. "Voucher yang Anda gunakan itu... di mana Anda menemukannya?"

Ia membeku.

"Karena," lanjutnya, sambil melirik tabletnya, "slip $5.000 itu dilaporkan hilang beberapa bulan yang lalu... dan itu bukan milik Anda."

Lampu di atas berkedip-kedip. Petugas keamanan muncul di tepi ruangan. Senyum Brettski memudar saat layar slot di sekitarnya mulai bermasalah‚Äîmenampilkan wajahnya di setiap monitor.

Bersambung‚Ä¶

Siapa Brettski? Brettski adalah seorang Penjudi Profesional, mirip dengan legenda kuno Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, TheBigJackpot, atau Lady Luck HQ! Namun, tidak seperti legenda-legenda ini, Brettski memiliki pengetahuan kuno yang tersimpan selama ribuan tahun, yang dikumpulkan oleh para tetua, dalam keterampilan seperti Mesin Slot, Roulette, Blackjack, Craps, Bubble Craps, Poker, dan Baccarat. Tujuan Brettski sebagai Penjudi Profesional sederhana: menguasai seluruh Las Vegas, menggunakan dana yang diperoleh dari Perjudian. Berlanggananlah untuk mendukung perjalanannya dalam mendominasi dunia.

Brettski couldn‚Äôt believe his eyes. Wedged between the seats of his old filming car‚Äîa crumpled $5,000 casino voucher from months ago. He stared at it, laughing in disbelief. ‚ÄúAin‚Äôt no way,‚Äù he muttered. The expiration date? Today. The universe had just thrown him a bone, or maybe a setup.

He raced to the casino, heart pounding like the bonus music on a Dragon Link. Cameras charged, mic clipped, that signature Brettski grin locked in. ‚ÄúLet‚Äôs see if the gambling gods are real,‚Äù he said, striding through the doors like a man on a mission.

His first machine? A $25 spin on Lightning Cash. Bang‚Äîbonus. $3,600 win. The crowd behind him started cheering. ‚ÄúHe‚Äôs back!‚Äù someone yelled. He switched to Buffalo Gold, dropped to $50 spins‚Äîdead spins. Then another. Then another. The $8,600 total melted to $4,200 in minutes.

‚ÄúOkay‚Ä¶ we‚Äôre in danger,‚Äù he whispered. Then, in pure Brettski fashion, he shoved the TITO slip into the high-limit room. A $100 bet per spin, eyes locked on the screen. Nothing. Then‚ÄîBANG‚Äîthree moons. Bonus. He leaned forward, eyes wide. Each spin added more moons, multipliers stacking. $1,000‚Ä¶ $3,000‚Ä¶ $9,000‚Ä¶ then the Grand symbol flashed once, twice‚Äî

‚Äîand disappeared.

The bonus ended at $14,700. Brettski threw his hands up. ‚ÄúThat‚Äôs the buyback money right there!‚Äù he laughed. He stood, ready to cash out, when the attendant walked over. ‚ÄúHey sir, quick question,‚Äù she said. ‚ÄúThat voucher you used‚Ä¶ where‚Äôd you find it?‚Äù

He froze.

‚ÄúBecause,‚Äù she continued, glancing at her tablet, ‚Äúthat $5,000 slip was reported missing months ago‚Ä¶ and it wasn‚Äôt yours.‚Äù

The lights above flickered. Security appeared at the edge of the room. Brettski‚Äôs smile faded as the slot screens around him began to glitch‚Äîshowing his face on every monitor.

snippet.title: Things are changing FAST..
snippet.description:
Asmongold Clips / Asmongold Reacts To: Kai Caenat friends goofin around 


On this Asmongold Clips Youtube Channel you'll never quit finding all the funny Asmongold Moments with Mcconnell and the best Asmongold Highlights from the most popular games, like: Baldur's Gate 3, Helldivers 2, Starfield, Blizzard Diablo 4, The War Within & Hardcore Classic WoW, the record breaking MMORPG FFXIV, Path of Exile 2, sneak peeks from Gameplay of the upcoming Riot MMO and playthroughs of many other popular games like Monster Hunter, Final Fantasy 16, Elden Ring and more. Also Asmongold Reacts to a lot of content, such as World Record Speed Run of games, Drama and videos of some of the most interesting creators like penguinz0, Internet Historian, Emiru, Dunkey and more. Asmon is also known for his "The True Story of Asmongold", "Asmongold $2 Pizza" and "Asmongold $2 Steak", "Asmongold Room and House Tour" videos, the legendary Transmog Competitions and Mount Off competitions, Ban Appeals, Media Share streams, Reddit Recap Reactions and much more.

‚ñ∫ Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/zackrawrr

#LetsGameItOut #OperaGX 

----------

Check it out on Steam ‚ñ∫ https://store.steampowered.com/app/641320/Cooking_Simulator/
And also the BBQ DLC ‚ñ∫ https://store.steampowered.com/app/3218770/Cooking_Simulator__BBQ/

More about Cooking Simulator (from Steam):
Become the ultimate chef! Take control of a highly polished, realistic kitchen equipped with all kinds of utensils and stands. Unlock and master over 80 recipes or use dozens of lifelike ingredients to cook everything you like. A simulator spiced up with a dash of real-life physics!

Key Features:
Career and Sandbox modes
80+ recipes
140+ lifelike ingredients
Perks and skills to unlock
Advanced cooking mechanics
Realistic physics

Your kitchen‚Äôs got all the gear a chef might need. Griddles, cookers, gas stands, ovens and tons of utensils like pots, pans, plates, knives, spatulas and blenders! On top of that there are over 140 ingredients available in the pantry: meat and fish, fruit and veggies, dairy products and various liquids. There‚Äôs also a full set of spices and herbs for adding that extra flavour!

Lifelike cooking experience! All the ingredients respond to your actions by changing temperature, appearance and taste. Every time you‚Äôre slicing potatoes, flipping steaks or boiling a soup, there are some real-life physics applied to it. Once you learn the cooking mechanics and start serving dishes, you‚Äôll see yourself becoming a better chef with every new plate on the checkout.

Career mode is a culinary journey zero-to-hero style and your task is to gain fame for you and your restaurant. You‚Äôll start from the basics and progressively unlock new more complex dishes and start serving more customers as your fame and experience grow. Once you master the recipes and workflow, you‚Äôll be able to unlock various perks and skills.

However, if you‚Äôre not interested in playing by the rules, you‚Äôre going to love the Sandbox mode. Access all the recipes and ingredients and prepare whatever you like without any pressure. You don‚Äôt even have to cook anything! Game physics gives you unlimited opportunities. Throw knives like darts, set up cutting boards like dominoes, set the whole kitchen on fire, blow up the oven and save the day using a fire extinguisher!

Fire up the grill and master the art of BBQ!
The hit Cooking Simulator expands outdoors with the BBQ DLC, turning your game into the ultimate BBQ restaurant simulator. Use realistic grilling techniques to serve tender brisket, juicy burgers, and sizzling ribs ‚Äî all set in a sun-soaked southern atmosphere.

About this DLC
Step outside the kitchen and into a brand-new outdoor cooking simulator experience. With gas and charcoal grills, tools, fryers, and custom crispness and aromatisation  techniques you‚Äôll discover what it takes to become a true grilmaster.

Cook with fire and fry, prepare your own stakes and burgers, glaze ribs to perfection, or fry up crispy bites. Whether you want to go low and slow BBQ or hot and fast grilling, every dish is yours to perfect.

Key Features
‚Ä¢ New BBQ restaurant ‚Äì A fully equipped outdoor kitchen with grills and fryers.

‚Ä¢ Meat preparing techniques ‚Äì Take care about crispiness, tenderness and aroma of your meat art

‚Ä¢ Authentic BBQ mechanics ‚Äì Grill, fry, and glaze with realistic cooking systems.

‚Ä¢ Fresh recipes & ingredients ‚Äì Burgers, brisket, ribs, chicken, and more.

‚Ä¢ Personalised BBQ dishes ‚Äì Build unique plates and wow your customers.

‚Ä¢ Atmospheric desert vibe ‚Äì Inspired by South BBQ culture.

Why BBQ DLC?
This expansion transforms Cooking Simulator into a realistic BBQ game. It‚Äôs more than just flipping burgers ‚Äî it‚Äôs about mastering the craft of outdoor cooking with fire, and flavour. The BBQ DLC adds depth, replayability, and smoky chaos to your favourite cooking game expansion.

Grab your tongs, light the coals, and prove you‚Äôre the BBQ master of Cooking Simulator.

And also the BBQ DLC ‚ñ∫ https://store.steampowered.com/app/3218770/Cooking_Simulator__BBQ/

More about Cooking Simulator (from Steam):
Become the ultimate chef! Take control of a highly polished, realistic kitchen equipped with all kinds of utensils and stands. Unlock and master over 80 recipes or use dozens of lifelike ingredients to cook everything you like. A simulator spiced up with a dash of real-life physics!

Key Features:
Career and Sandbox modes
80+ recipes
140+ lifelike ingredients
Perks and skills to unlock
Advanced cooking mechanics
Realistic physics

Your kitchen‚Äôs got all the gear a chef might need. Griddles, cookers, gas stands, ovens and tons of utensils like pots, pans, plates, knives, spatulas and blenders! On top of that there are over 140 ingredients available in the pantry: meat and fish, fruit and veggies, dairy products and various liquids. There‚Äôs also a full set of spices and herbs for adding that extra flavour!

Lifelike cooking experience! All the ingredients respond to your actions by changing temperature, appearance and taste. Every time you‚Äôre slicing potatoes, flipping steaks or boiling a soup, there are some real-life physics applied to it. Once you learn the cooking mechanics and start serving dishes, you‚Äôll see yourself becoming a better chef with every new plate on the checkout.

Career mode is a culinary journey zero-to-hero style and your task is to gain fame for you and your restaurant. You‚Äôll start from the basics and progressively unlock new more complex dishes and start serving more customers as your fame and experience grow. Once you master the recipes and workflow, you‚Äôll be able to unlock various perks and skills.

However, if you‚Äôre not interested in playing by the rules, you‚Äôre going to love the Sandbox mode. Access all the recipes and ingredients and prepare whatever you like without any pressure. You don‚Äôt even have to cook anything! Game physics gives you unlimited opportunities. Throw knives like darts, set up cutting boards like dominoes, set the whole kitchen on fire, blow up the oven and save the day using a fire extinguisher!

Fire up the grill and master the art of BBQ!
The hit Cooking Simulator expands outdoors with the BBQ DLC, turning your game into the ultimate BBQ restaurant simulator. Use realistic grilling techniques to serve tender brisket, juicy burgers, and sizzling ribs ‚Äî all set in a sun-soaked southern atmosphere.

About this DLC
Step outside the kitchen and into a brand-new outdoor cooking simulator experience. With gas and charcoal grills, tools, fryers, and custom crispness and aromatisation  techniques you‚Äôll discover what it takes to become a true grilmaster.

Cook with fire and fry, prepare your own stakes and burgers, glaze ribs to perfection, or fry up crispy bites. Whether you want to go low and slow BBQ or hot and fast grilling, every dish is yours to perfect.

Key Features
‚Ä¢ New BBQ restaurant ‚Äì A fully equipped outdoor kitchen with grills and fryers.

‚Ä¢ Meat preparing techniques ‚Äì Take care about crispiness, tenderness and aroma of your meat art

‚Ä¢ Authentic BBQ mechanics ‚Äì Grill, fry, and glaze with realistic cooking systems.

‚Ä¢ Fresh recipes & ingredients ‚Äì Burgers, brisket, ribs, chicken, and more.

‚Ä¢ Personalised BBQ dishes ‚Äì Build unique plates and wow your customers.

‚Ä¢ Atmospheric desert vibe ‚Äì Inspired by South BBQ culture.

Why BBQ DLC?
This expansion transforms Cooking Simulator into a realistic BBQ game. It‚Äôs more than just flipping burgers ‚Äî it‚Äôs about mastering the craft of outdoor cooking with fire, and flavour. The BBQ DLC adds depth, replayability, and smoky chaos to your favourite cooking game expansion.

Grab your tongs, light the coals, and prove you‚Äôre the BBQ master of Cooking Simulator.

ARC Raiders 2025 Gameplay Walkthrough will include a Review, Reaction, Prologue Intro (Opening), Solo Gameplay, Guide (Tips and Tricks), Loot, Skill Tree, Combat, Character Creation, Cinematics, Cut Scenes, Soundtrack (OST) and the Full Story (Lore). snippet.title: Horrifying Reddit Threads
snippet.description:
From a 'replaced brother' to a disturbing upstairs neighbor, these are some Horrifying Reddit Threads. These stories are truly some of the most disturbing and sad stories I've ever read, I hope every OP in this video is doing better now. Would you like to see me make similar videos in the future? Leave your thoughts down below in the comment section, and make sure to like and subscribe!

Timestamps:

0:00 | Intro
0:44 | I believe my brother has been 'replaced'
14:21 | OP is certain her upstairs neighbor is stalking her through unknown means
30:53 | My husband killed someone and can't cope
38:31 | Found an abandoned car in the woods and it looked like something bad maybe happened
42:42 | I have 2 weeks to get away from my husband
56:00 | OP's dad went missing, and the police are being hostile to her attempts to get answers
1:06:35 | Can anyone help with type of shoe left this print outside my daughter's window?
1:15:50 | My elderly mom is hospice and her new "friend" gives me a bad vibe
1:29:41 | Who could possibly have spare keys to my house?
1:36:56 | Outro

Make sure to subscribe to the Patreon for early access videos and many more perks! https://www.patreon.com/SnookYT

And yes, I'm a human voice.

If your story or post was included in today's video and you wish for it to be taken down, please reach out to this email. Officialsnook23@gmail.com 

Channel sub goal is 1 million subscribers! So subscribe!
